today has been the most perfect whirlwind of a day

After four long years, I've finally come to the end of my bachelor's degree. Along the way, I've made many friends. Some I've known all four years; others, I've met just this semester. I couldn't take pictures with everyone, but you are all in my heart. This journey would've been so much harder without you. I'm thankful for my supportive parents as well... My friends, we go forth unto our next journey. It will be scary and difficult but as Mellody Hobson said, "Just add bravery". We go forth as Trojans. Brilliant and bold. Ever instilled with the energy to do great things. Fight on, class of 2015.
